{"tid":2097394,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk於Tesla官網推出「特斯拉沽空短褲」（Tesla Short Shorts）諷刺沽空者","createTime":"2020-07-06T19:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T08:25:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":129,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b77c892936d1c6ec9b08c1cde9b2f09d36dbde0b","tid":2097394,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:29:59.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕電動車廠特斯拉（Tesla）最近幾個月股價飆漲，從3月中每股360美元反彈至本月2日的1208.66美元，甚至超越豐田（Toyota）成為世界市值最高車廠；由於特斯拉過去以來放空者眾，素來直言不諱且花招百出的執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）也沒放過此機會，順勢推出艷紅色的「特斯拉放空短褲」（Tesla Short Shorts），以嘲諷那些放空者。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克在5日發佈的推文中，放上特斯拉購物網站連結，表示該「放空短褲」已上架開賣，馬斯克還在推文強調這是「限量品」，每件要價69.420美元（約新台幣2060元）；官網形容該產品「如風般馳騁」，可整年地在「湖畔或lounge放鬆身心」，並「享受收盤鐘後的無比快意」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3219920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3219920&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=d9893075\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3219920&h=94ab0901\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3219920</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.tesla.com/product/tesla-short-shorts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.tesla.com%2Fproduct%2Ftesla-short-shorts&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=be9fb7a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.tesla.com/product/tesla-short-shorts</a>"},{"pid":"a34f0ba60eaae03ea32ef1ded6630b0b29355fab","tid":2097394,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd6b61331a69254d7fbe1625f18ef1eb929acae","t